{"name": "odoo-addon-shopinvader-api-delivery-carrier", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-shopinvader-api-delivery-carrier", "version": "16.0.1.1.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader-carrier", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["extendable-pydantic", "fastapi", "odoo-addon-delivery-carrier-info", "odoo-addon-extendable", "odoo-addon-extendable-fastapi", "odoo-addon-fastapi", "odoo-addon-pydantic", "odoo-addon-queue-job", "odoo-addon-sale-discount-display-amount", "odoo-addon-sale-shipping-info-helper", "odoo-addon-shopinvader-api-cart", "odoo-addon-shopinvader-api-security-sale", "odoo-addon-shopinvader-delivery-carrier", "odoo-addon-shopinvader-filtered-model", "odoo-addon-shopinvader-sale-cart", "odoo-addon-shopinvader-schema-sale", "odoo", "pydantic"], "summary": "Carrier integration for Shopinvader", "upload_time": 1717595304}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Alpha-red.png\n    :alt: Alpha\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-shopinvader%2Fodoo--shopinvader--carrier-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader-carrier\n    :target: https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader-carrier/tree/16.0/shopinvader_api_delivery_carrier\n    ```\n---\n\n# Shopinvader Carrier\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:938a463d8336563006a6b2e4d7e5f25f26e2d9f171b78a0032b271e8784f6044\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }}\n\nAdd the configuration and the logic to manage the carrier on your ShopInvader site\n\n:::{IMPORTANT}\nThis is an alpha version, the data model and design can change at any time without warning.\nOnly for development or testing purpose, do not use in production.\n[More details on development status](https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status)\n:::\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nThis module will give you several endpoints for interacting with delivery carrier.\nYou can play with it with swagger.\n\nThis module provides the following routers:\n\\* `delivery_carrier_router` to get the carriers available for a partner;\n\\* `delivery_carrier_cart_router` to get the carriers available for a cart, including delivery prices for the cart, and set a carrier on a cart;\n\\* `delivery_router`: to search on all deliveries linked to the authenticated partner.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader-carrier/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader-carrier/issues/new?body=module:%20shopinvader_api_delivery_carrier%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Akretion\n- Acsone SA/NV\n- Shopinvader\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Sebastien BEAU \\<<mailto:sebastien.beau@akretion.com>>\n- Benoit GUILLOT \\<<mailto:benoit.guillot@akretion.com>>\n- Laurent MIGNON \\<<mailto:laurent.mignon@acsone.eu>>\n- C\u00e9dric PIGEON \\<<mailto:cedric.pigeon@acsone.eu>>\n- Denis ROUSSEL \\<<mailto:denis.roussel@acsone.eu>>\n- Simone Orsi \\<<mailto:simone.orsi@camptocamp.com>>\n- Marie Lejeune \\<<mailto:marie.lejeune@acsone.eu>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is part of the [shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader-carrier](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader-carrier/tree/16.0/shopinvader_api_delivery_carrier) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_delivery_carrier.tests.test_sale_deliveries", "documentation": ["Copyright 2020 Camptocamp SA", "Copyright 2023 ACSONE SA/NV", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_delivery_carrier.tests.test_sale_deliveries.TestSaleDeliveries", "bases": ["TestShopinvaderDeliveryCarrierCommon"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_delivery_carrier.tests.test_sale_deliveries.TestSaleDeliveries.setUpClass", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cls", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_delivery_carrier.tests.test_sale_deliveries.TestSaleDeliveries._confirm_and_deliver_sale", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_delivery_carrier.tests.test_sale_deliveries.TestSaleDeliveries.test_read_sale", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_api_delivery_carrier.tests", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_ap